        "created_at": "2024-12-15T14:45:15.657Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Disable gif/sticker animations already requested here:</p>\n<aside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"4\" data-topic=\"19186\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/ramxtr/48/16257_2.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/stop-animated-stickers-and-gifs/19186/4\">Stop animated stickers and gifs</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/17\"><span data-category-id=\"17\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #83B72A; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category \" title=\"Post your ideas here for new features and functionality for the Signal app.\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    It would be nice if gifs and animated stickers would stop from endlessly replaying and looping. At some point these animations become too distracting. \nFor reference, WhatsApp plays a gif twice I believe and then just stops, and pressing on the gif will result in replaying that gif only for the user pressing on the gif.\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n\n<p>Disable UI transitions already requested, but you can do it from the OS level:</p>\n<aside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"52785\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/hacxman/48/32514_2.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/option-to-turn-off-all-animations/52785\">Option to turn off all animations</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/17\"><span data-category-id=\"17\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #83B72A; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category \" title=\"Post your ideas here for new features and functionality for the Signal app.\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    Hi, Iâ€™d like to kindly request an option in settings to completely disable all UI animations. \nMaybe except stickers, those could be controlled separately, idk. \nIm very sensitive to those (animations). I find animated software very hard and unpleasant to use. \nPlease, think about it. It is very important accessibility feature. \nThanks\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n",
